==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Paludal
<hw>Pa*lu"dal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>palus</ets>, <ets>-udis</ets>, a marsh.]</ety> <def>Of or
pertaining to marshes or fens; marshy.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Paludal fever</b></col>, <cd>malarial fever; -- so called
because generated in marshy districts.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Paludament</ent>⟦br⟧
